{"questionId":"3070460","questionHtml":"<p>Hence or otherwise, determine the exact values of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi></math> such that AS-quadratic functions are formed.</p>\n<p>Give your answers in the form&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>p</mi><mo>±</mo><mi>q</mi><msqrt><mi>s</mi></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math> where <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi></math>, <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>s</mi><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℤ</mi><mo>+</mo></msup></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p>substitutes their expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math> with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math> into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Q</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Q</mi><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>⇒</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></math></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>b</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p>substitutes their expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math> with&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math> into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Q</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Q</mi><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>⇒</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></math></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math> (seen anywhere)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p>\n<p>attempts to solve their quadratic in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>substitutes into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>4</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A0A0</strong></em> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi></math> expressed as decimal values.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award a maximum of <em><strong>(M1)A1(M1)A0A0FT</strong></em> for <em><strong>FT</strong></em> from part (g) (i).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p>substitutes their expressions for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math> and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math> with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math> into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Q</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced></mrow></mfenced><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>32</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>1</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math> (seen anywhere)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>8</mn></mfrac><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>32</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p>\n<p>attempts to solve their quadratic in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>substitutes into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>4</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A0A0</strong></em> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi></math> expressed as decimal values.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award a maximum of <em><strong>(M1)A1(M1)A0A0FT</strong></em> for <em><strong>FT</strong></em> from part (g) (i).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 3</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>b</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p>substitutes their expressions for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math> and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math> with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math> into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>c</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mstyle></mrow></mfrac></math> (or equivalent)</p>\n<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math> (seen anywhere) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong><br>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong><br>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></p>\n<p>attempts to solve their quadratic in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>substitutes into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>4</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A0A0</strong></em> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi></math> expressed as decimal values.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award a maximum of <em><strong>(M1)A1(M1)A0A0FT</strong></em> for <em><strong>FT</strong></em> from part (g) (i).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 4</strong></p>\n<p>attempts to equate two expressions for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math> with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>±</mo><msqrt><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>c</mi></msqrt></mrow><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mo>±</mo><msqrt><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>c</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math> (seen anywhere)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>12</mn><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>32</mn><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math> <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></math></p>\n<p>attempts to solve their quadratic in <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>substitutes into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>±</mo><mn>4</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A0A0</strong></em> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi></math> expressed as decimal values.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award a maximum of <em><strong>(M1)A1(M1)A0A0FT</strong></em> for <em><strong>FT</strong></em> from part (g) (i).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 5</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>d</mi><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>substitutes their expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math> in terms of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>d</mi></math>with <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math> into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Q</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Q</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>⇒</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>d</mi><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>(</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></math></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>d</mi><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>substitutes their expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>&nbsp;in terms of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>d</mi></math> with&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac>